          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-981-15W1-line-1" n="1">P<hi rend="small-caps">ERLEGI</hi> versus versos, Jonathan bone, tersos;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-981-15W1-line-2" n="2">Perlepidos quidèm; scribendo semper es idem.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-981-15W1-line-3" n="3">Laudibus extollo te, tu mihi magnus Apollo;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-981-15W1-line-4" n="4">Tu frater Phœbus, oculis collyria præbes,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-981-15W1-line-5" n="5">Ne minus insanæ reparas quoque damna Dianæ,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-981-15W1-line-6" n="6">Quæ me percussit radiis (nec dixeris ussit)</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-981-15W1-line-7" n="7">Frigore collecto; medicus moderamine tecto</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-981-15W1-line-8" n="8">Lodicum binum permit, et negatis mihi vinum.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-981-15W1-line-9" n="9">O terra et cœlum! quàm redit pectus anhelum.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-981-15W1-line-10" n="10">Os mihi jam siccum, liceat mihi bibere dic cum?</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-981-15W1-line-11" n="11">Ex vestro grato poculo, tam sæpe prolato,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-981-15W1-line-12" n="12">Vina crepant: sales ostendet quis mihi tales?</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-981-15W1-line-13" n="13">Lumina, vos sperno, dum cuppæ gaudia cerno:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-981-15W1-line-14" n="14">Perdere etenim pellem nostram, quoque crura mavellem.</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-981-15W1-line-15" n="15">Amphora. quam dulces risus queis pectora mulces,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-981-15W1-line-16" n="16">Pangitur a Flacco, cum pectus turget Iaccho:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-981-15W1-line-17" n="17">Clarius evohe ingeminans geminatur et ohe;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-981-15W1-line-18" n="18">Nempe jocosa propago, hesit sic vocis imago.</l>
          </lg>
